# Ephemeral work artifacts in repo ROOT (Artifact Storage Rule).
# Root-anchored (leading /) — only repo root, so files in subdirs are unaffected.
# Durable products of work → work/<stream>/ (tracked); ephemeral/scratch → here or scratchpad.
/_tmp_*
/.tmp-*
/*.tmp
